{
  "stem": "8569.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Don't create panic of these warmongers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And don't disturb your mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So whether he knew and tried to deny it, I couldn't tell you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And whether my mother knew, I couldn't tell you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But we knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I think that this was the beginning of the seed of the Warsaw ghetto rebellion, this particular meeting.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I continue going to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I remember also it must have been in 1942, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when the allied forces entered the war, there was a blackout.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And in Warsaw ghetto, it was all dark.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And people were walking around on the street with phosphorous little [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] pins so that they could see each other walking.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Otherwise, you couldn't see anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In Warsaw ghetto was at that time a terrible, terrible hunger.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It was-- it was indescribable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was no food coming in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was no food in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The rations that were received were not sufficient for anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was enough to have two pieces of bread per day, which you had supplement with potatoes if you could get it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There were children whose parents were transported out, orphans on the streets.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And you could see them from day to day sitting on the streets, getting thinner and thinner, and then suddenly getting bigger.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "When they were in the last stage of the hunger, they were-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I don't-- they were bloated.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they used to die on the street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I remember one day when my sister and I were walking on the street, and she bought some detergent for washing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the young-- and we were walking through.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "This was wrapped up.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
